name: Pom's Sketchbook #01: "Elizabeth"
description: I'm a big fan of simple sketches. When I really like the linework I do on one, sometimes, I'm hesitant to go too wild with colour and shading-- this was one of these cases. I added a simple open-source watercolour texture and toyed with a few palette options, then left it as is. I hope you enjoy it, even if it's not as "produced" as some of my work.
